{"tid":1488871,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：係時候清算泛民","createTime":"2019-08-19T17:15:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T22:20:28.000Z","uid":157994,"like":30,"dislike":184,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"204252da9e5faac7742a9e59a37e16292df6afab","tid":1488871,"uid":157994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:15:23.000Z","msg":"陳雲：兄弟爬山，就不要在後面扯口罩、脫褲子。我們仍未成功，泛民昨日就宣布贏了，因為我們擺脫了他們，繼續前進，攀登更高的山，他們只能說已經到了終點，說可以除口罩相認了。<br />\n這些在最後一步才用直升機加入登山的泛民，被我們擺脫了。他們一直想脫了我們的口罩，甚至褲子，不過這不會阻止我們向雙普選邁進，甚至向普選之後的高山邁進。<br />\n這幅圖，列出了泛民在抗爭前傳的所作所為。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZycXqNT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZycXqNT.png&h=a378923a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n國師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />國師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />國師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />國師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de4309667d4bcbb6b9bf4bb8d5646ba5877aed13","tid":1488871,"uid":23953,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:16:17.000Z","msg":"荃灣被斬示威者<br />\n左腳傷勢：<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/z0k1UL0.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz0k1UL0.jpg&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NADQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=1a90393d\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/z0k1UL0.jpg</a><br />\n右手傷勢：<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/oeH3751.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoeH3751.jpg&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NADQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=52007f21\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/oeH3751.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n爆眼<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/eye-10_1OhWT_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Feye-10_1OhWT_1200x0.png&h=05e4a6ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n門牙爆裂<br />\n<img src